Text: Moore's done it again. This was wicked.
Thanks for ul! I was wondering what happened after #8.

Thank you so much for this! I'm buying hard copies of these as I find them too. May I make a request for Dodgem Logic? I hope those make their way to this side of the Atlantic and Moore continues to be able to do underground work which is also (physically) accessible.

shexxy, here's Dodgem Logic #1-8 published by Southern Print.  #1 is c2c and issues 2-8 have just the Alan Moore content.
